VRF_COORDINATOR().notice: parameters for requesting random words from Chainlink VRF

acceptCase(uint256).notice: drawn mediator may accept a case by staking an amount equal to the mediatorFlatFee

appeal(uint256).notice: creates new 'appeal' dispute with project/dispute information from original dispute   mediation fee is higher to compensate larger panel

assignAdditionalMediators(uint256,addres.notice: assigns additional addresses to drawnMediators in Panel

assignArbiter(uint256,address).notice: assigns an arbiter to a deadlocked case to break the tie

breakTie(uint256,bool).notice: assigned arbiter breaks tie on a deadlocked case

claimMediatorFees().notice: withdraw fees earned for serving on panel

dismissUnpaidCase(uint256).notice: closes a Dispute when mediation fees have not been paid within DISCOVER_PERIODa dismissed case will return to original project fee amount in Marketplace

drawAdditionalMediators(uint256).notice: draws additional mediators if not enough mediators have accepted case after PANEL_SELECTION_PERIOD elapses

mediatorFlatFee().notice: the amount that will be paid to mediators who vote in the majoritymediators must stake an amount equal to mediatorFlatFee to accept a case

overdueCommit(uint256).notice: removes mediator who does not commit vote within VOTING_PERIODtransfers stake of overdue mediator to Panel Reserve

overdueReveal(uint256).notice: removes mediators who fail to reveal hidden vote during REVEAL_PERIODremoved mediator's stake will be forfeitted and transferred to Panel Reserveif a majority can still be reached without the overdue mediator's vote, a decision will be renderedif the votes are tied, an arbiter may be assigned by Nebulai to break the tie

payMediationFee(uint256,string[]).notice: pay mediation fee and submit evidencewhen both disputants have paid, random words will be requested and mediator panel will be drawn

reclaimMediationFee(uint256).notice: allows revailing party to reclaim mediation fee after mediation is complete

requestDefaultDecision(uint256).notice: rules in favor disputant who paid mediation fee when one disputant has not paid within DISCLOSURE_PERIOD

revealVote(uint256,bool,string).notice: mediator reveals hidden vote and mediator stake is returned

submitAdditionalEvidence(uint256,string[.notice: allows disputants who have paid mediation fee to submit additional evidenceevidence can only be submitted during Disclosure and Panel Selection
